        english_translation: 'O Auspicious One! May your mass of hair—dense, glossy, and smooth, like a forest of full-blown blue lotuses—dispel our inner darkness. I believe that the flowers from Indra\'s celestial garden reside in it only to absorb its natural fragrance.',
        commentary: 'The Goddess\'s hair is described as being so beautiful and fragrant that even celestial flowers desire to be in it to gain their own scent. Meditating on it is said to remove spiritual ignorance.'
